Dairy, processed sugar, wheat/gluten, and whey protein powders are common acne triggers. You don’t need to completely deprive yourself of all of the above for clear skin, it’s just that limiting those foods makes a huge difference for alot of my clients that suffer from acne.

Know the difference between different acne-related problems ✨

Cystic acne is the toughest type of acne to deal with, cysts develop deep underneath your skin and they are often accompanied with pain. Cystic acne tends to leave scarring behind too, so it’s very important to know how to deal with this type of acne.
